nd and assigns the result to the left operand.|||Ex: C -= A is equivalent to C = C - A|||&&&4|||*= (Multiply and Assignment)|||It multiplies the right operand with the left operand and assigns the result to the left operand.|||Ex: C *= A is equivalent to C = C * A|||&&&5|||/= (Divide and Assignment)|||It divides the left operand with the right operand and assigns the result to the left operand.|||Ex: C /= A is equivalent to C = C / A|||&&&6|||%= (Modules and Assignment)|||It takes modulus using two operands and assigns the result to the left operand.|||Ex: C %= A is equivalent to C = C % A|||\', \'Sr.No.|||Operator and Description&&&1|||? : (Conditional )|||If Condition is true? Then value X : Otherwise value Y|||\', \'Type|||String Returned by typeof&&&Number|||\"number\"&&&String|||\"string\"&&&Boolean|||\"boolean\"&&&Object|||\"object\"&&&Function|||\"function\"&&&Undefined|||\"undefined\"&&&Null|||\"object\"\']','[\'Arithmetic Operators|||Comparison Operators|||Logical (or Relational) Operators|||Assignment Operators|||Conditional (or ternary) Operators|||\']'),(7,'[\'JavaScript - if...else Statement\']','[\'Flow Chart of if-else\', \'if statement\', \'if...else statement\', \'if...else if... statement\', \'Useful Video Courses\']','[\'Syntax\', \'Example\', \'Output\', \'Syntax\', \'Example\', \'Output\', \'Syntax\', \'Example\', \'Output\']','[\'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript/javascript_operators.htm\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript/javascript_switch_case.htm\', \'http://tpcg.io/phmRNV\', \'http://tpcg.io/B5GzT5\', \'http://tpcg.io/NTcFyX\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/profile/Anadi-Sharma\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_for_beginners/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_for_beginn