\'t react at all...</p>\n      <a href = \"javascript:void(alert(\'Warning!!!\'))\">Click me!</a>     \n   </body>\n</html>\n\', \'\n<html>\n   <head>   \n      <script type = \"text/javascript\">\n         <!--\n         //-->\n      </script>      \n   </head>\n   \n   <body>   \n      <p>Click the following, This won\'t react at all...</p>\n      <a href = \"javascript:void(0)\">Click me!</a>      \n   </body>\n</html>\n\', \'\n<html>\n   <head>      \n      <script type = \"text/javascript\">\n         <!--\n            function getValue() {\n               var a,b,c;\n               \n               a = void ( b = 5, c = 7 );\n               document.write(\'a = \' + a + \' b = \' + b +\' c = \' + c );\n            }\n         //-->\n      </script>      \n   </head>\n   \n   <body>\n      <p>Click the following to see the result:</p>\n      <form>\n         <input type = \"button\" value = \"Click Me\" onclick = \"getValue();\" />\n      </form>     \n   </body>\n</html>\n\']','[\'\n<head>\n   <script type = \"text/javascript\">\n      <!--\n         void func()\n         javascript:void func()\n         or:\n         void(func())\n         javascript:void(func())\n      //-->\n   </script>\n</head>\n\']','[]','[]'),(19,'[\'JavaScript - Page Printing\']','[\'How to Print a Page?\', \'Useful Video Courses\']','[\'Example\', \'Output\']','[\'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript/javascript_void_keyword.htm\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript/javascript_objects.htm\', \'http://tpcg.io/8GxlA1\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript/printfriendly.htm\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/profile/Anadi-Sharma\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_online_training/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_for_beginners/index.asp\', \'https://www.tutorialspoint.com/javascript_for_be